title: Letzte Instanz - Kalter Glanz
description:
Hey guys: it's July 15th 2009. FYI, I still seed this torrent almost all of the time. I have about a 200x share ratio, and I will NOT be stopping anytime soon. Even if you're just curious about them, please download. These guys are amazing and I want to spread the wealth!


This is the 2001 album "Kalter Glanz" by the band Letzte Instanz. It took me about two months of looking for it online to find it, so when I did, naturally, I uploaded it here. I will be seeding this torrent whenever my computer is on. Period. If you can't download it, then leave the torrent in your downloads for a couple of days, and I'll be on for at least six hours during that; this album was hard to get, and it's damn worthwhile, so whenever I'm online this torrent gets top priority.

I HIGHLY recommend this band. I live in the middle of New Mexico, so I've had to import several of their albums, but it's definitely worth it. If you like them, I believe they're now listed on Amazon.com (used to only be on amazon.de), and they're worth supporting.
